data.description: MOVE-IN READY!  This two-story, beautiful home is located in the gated Preserve at Alamo Ranch community. Soaring ceilings lead to an open floor plan with private study, living room, dining room & gourmet kitchen, all perfect for entertaining friends & family. Relax on the upgraded (2020) extended patio perfect for cookouts & enjoying peaceful evenings. Main level multi generational living is a breeze with 2 bedrooms downstairs, the expansive Primary bedroom & second bedroom with private full bathroom. Bonus rooms include a game room loft & media room upstairs for two more additional living spaces, study space & more entertainment. Neighborhood amenities feature pool & park/playground areas. Ask realtor for updates. Must see home that shows like a model home & is the perfect balance of tranquility & convenience! Close to dining, shopping, parks, & easy highway access.
